arguments.template:
<ng-container [formGroup]="group">

    <ngb-datepicker [displayMonths]="model.getAdditional('displayMonths', config['displayMonths'])"
                    [dynamicId]="bindId && model.id"
                    [firstDayOfWeek]="model.getAdditional('firstDayOfWeek', config['firstDayOfWeek'])"
                    [formControlName]="model.id"
                    [maxDate]="model.max"
                    [minDate]="model.min"
                    [navigation]="model.getAdditional('navigation', config['navigation'])"
                    [ngClass]="getClass('element', 'control')"
                    [outsideDays]="model.getAdditional('outsideDays', config['outsideDays'])"
                    [showWeekdays]="model.getAdditional('showWeekdays', config['showWeekdays'])"
                    [showWeekNumbers]="model.getAdditional('showWeekNumbers', config['showWeekNumbers'])"
                    [startDate]="model.focusedDate"
                    (select)="onChange($event)"></ngb-datepicker>

</ng-container>

<ng-container [formGroup]="group">

    <select class="form-control"
            [class.is-invalid]="showErrorMessages"
            [compareWith]="model.compareWithFn"
            [dynamicId]="bindId && model.id"
            [formControlName]="model.id"
            [name]="model.name"
            [ngClass]="getClass('element', 'control')"
            [required]="model.required"
            [tabindex]="model.tabIndex"
            (blur)="onBlur($event)"
            (change)="onChange($event)"
            (focus)="onFocus($event)">

        <option *ngFor="let option of model.options$ | async"
                [disabled]="option.disabled"
                [ngValue]="option.value">{{ option.label }}</option>

    </select>

</ng-container>

<ng-container [formGroup]="group">

    <ngb-timepicker [dynamicId]="bindId && model.id"
                    [formControlName]="model.id"
                    [hourStep]="model.getAdditional('hourStep', config['hourStep'])"
                    [meridian]="model.meridian"
                    [minuteStep]="model.getAdditional('minuteStep', config['minuteStep'])"
                    [ngClass]="getClass('element', 'control')"
                    [seconds]="model.showSeconds"
                    [secondStep]="model.getAdditional('secondStep', config['secondStep'])"
                    [size]="model.getAdditional('size', config['size'])"
                    [spinners]="model.getAdditional('spinners', config['spinners'])"></ngb-timepicker>

</ng-container>

<dynamic-ng-bootstrap-form-control *ngFor="let model of formModel; trackBy: trackByFn"
                                   [group]="formGroup"
                                   [hidden]="model.hidden"
                                   [layout]="formLayout"
                                   [model]="model"
                                   [ngClass]="[getClass(model, 'element', 'host'), getClass(model, 'grid', 'host')]"
                                   [templates]="templates"
                                   (blur)="onEvent($event, 'blur')"
                                   (change)="onEvent($event, 'change')"
                                   (focus)="onEvent($event, 'focus')"
                                   (click)="onEvent($event, 'focus')"
                                   (ngbEvent)="onEvent($event, 'custom')"></dynamic-ng-bootstrap-form-control>
{{ message }}
